---
title: Grilled Chicken Fajitas with Charred Corn and Creamy Chipotle Sauce
description: Charred corn and grilled, spiced chicken tenders add a delicious smokiness to these fajitas. To make things even easier on a weeknight, grab an oven-proof pan and cook the veggies on the grill top, too!
